Subject:

    You have to create a module named "myfirstclass.py" which will contain
    a class which will implements:

        * a constructor which will take a string as parameter and store her

        * a method called hashIt which will have a kwarg called hash
	  and take a callable as parameter and will return the hash of the
	  string in the class returned by the callable

        * a static method called hashParam which will take a string as
	  parameter and a kwarg called hash which should be a callable and
	  return the hash of the string in parameter returned by the callable

        * hint: static method, kwarg, callable, class
